HEADWORD: outside-group
<hw>outside-group</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to marriage
outside a class or tribe, in cultures where that is required by custom
or law.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> exogamic.</syn>⟦br⟧
